return {title = "Spindown Dice", id = "723", description = {'Rerolls all pedestal items, lowering all their internal item IDs by 1', "Items that are yet to be unlocked will also be skipped over, preventing you from getting items you don't have access to yet", 'There are some gaps in item IDs which are skipped if no item exists, or will reroll into unexpected items if hidden items are present at that ID. For example rerolling Plan C (ID = 475) changes it into the Broken Glass Cannon, which is a hidden item with ID = 474', 'Sad Onion (ID = 1) will reroll into nothing', "For example: Brimstone's ID = 118, so it would be rerolled into Dead Bird (ID = 117)"}}